{"tid":1777821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本高中生網購鈾提煉出售","createTime":"2019-12-10T13:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T13:37:04.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93e65eb2e8e40209d820ae24c24b5f936d94b776","tid":1777821,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"日本警視廳表示，東京小金井市1名17歲男高中生，於網路上購買鈾並疑似提煉成黃色粉末出售，目前已依違反「核子反應爐管制法」和「毒物及有害物質取締法」等罪嫌送辦。<br />\n <br />\n據《NHK》報導，除了高中生之外，另有長野縣24歲男子和茨城縣6    1歲男子都購買了鈾，日本核子管制委員會於11月查覺有異，警方隨即前往3人家中並順利搜出鈾，幸好其輻射相當微量，對人體不會造成任何傷害。<br />\n <br />\n被移送法辦的3人都是化學愛好者，高中生更強調自己只是想要收藏而已，但警方發現高中生疑似向海外賣家購入鈾後，再將鈾礦研製成黃色粉末放到拍賣網站上試圖出售。<br />\n <br />\n鈾是一種放射性物質，可以用作核武器的原料，將天然鈾礦除去雜質進行濃縮純化的產物稱為「黃餅」。不過，高中生研製物質的純度和「黃餅」相去甚遠。<br />\n <br />\n日本「核子反應爐管制法」規定，未經核子管制委員會的許可，出售鈾或購買鈾都是違法的，最高可處1年有期徒刑或100萬日元罰款（約新台幣28萬元）。"},{"pid":"42bc5180ecfda199edcf9a9a1d13feb6aadf71d2","tid":1777821,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:24:15.000Z","msg":"炸佢老母西<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611300d8448427e71f3c176e88a1221ddea30c5a","tid":1777821,"uid":20924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"sheldon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a333c28da0a3452db974d5a7d52c6384fdccde","tid":1777821,"uid":144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"鈾238<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"efbb41e7db99b432e72e872a2094141435896c85","tid":1777821,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:26:16.000Z","msg":"用手fing <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"f73a3224b64d228d2f821b68e939ef727755eb1b","tid":1777821,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起上年個日本妹寫咗幾行JAVASCRIPT搞到人地熄唔到BROWSER比人拉撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b61a6bf07c36defe74ae4520aea4967128a6cca","tid":1777821,"uid":105578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"高中生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}